&lt;p&gt;Previously, we had announced the first Meetup would be on June 20, but weren&amp;rsquo;t sure where. We are happy to say that the &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.innevation.com/&#34;&gt;Innevation Center, Powered by Switch&lt;/a&gt; has agreed to host us (no spelling error, &amp;ldquo;nev&amp;rdquo; as in Nevada). The agenda will remain the same: an intro to the group and an introduction to Python and R for data analysis, especially for Excel users.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We&amp;rsquo;ll start at 6:30, and there will be free food. There is no charge to attend, or reservations required, so we hope you&amp;rsquo;ll bring a colleague along.&lt;/p&gt;

